    • Constructor Detail

      • PSRWriter

        public PSRWriter(int mode,
         java.lang.String file,
         processing.core.PApplet app)
        Parameters:
        mode - If is set to PSRWriter.PSR_PASIVE, it wont recreate any graphics. If is set to PSRWriter.PSR_ACTIVE, it would recreate parsed commands in the spesified PApplet.
        file - The path to the .psr output file.
        app - The PApplet of your sketch.
